uring the absolute deviation of the share of the commodity i in total exports (or imports) of the country from the share of the commodity i in total world export (or imports). Thus, the lower the index the closer is the country\u2019s structure of trade to the world\u2019s structure of trade. An index value closer to one indicates a bigger difference from the world average.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "fb4de188-712f-4a9a-9d86-be27c7a81fa4": {"__data__": {"id_": "fb4de188-712f-4a9a-9d86-be27c7a81fa4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2006-trade-human-terms", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development Report 2006: Trade on Human Terms", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2006-trade-human-terms", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "d39b689f8bf552402133e5228efa843a10031cb8a03dc09cf2404213ba171ff9"}, "2": {"node_id": "a9b128e0-be66-4041-86e7-38493420b8de", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2006-trade-human-terms", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "12ebc68a5a836d454a36a015e68771b4137949b19e106e76733026e35f5a2ef7"}}, "hash": "1215bbef96ce0532518d63dd682c0d5d7169367ae656a789a26eb4505ba9fb15", "text": "An index value closer to one indicat